Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic is disappearing\Nall across Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we learn about a\Ncreature that{\i1} eats{\i0} magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony should investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought\NStarlight Glimmer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.08,0:00:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,was going to be\Ntemporary Head Mare.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With Equestria under attack,\NPonies must stand together!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I need the Cutie Mark Crusaders!\NMy friends are in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems my little protégé's\Nplan worked after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The future empress\Nof friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Cozy Glow is\Nbehind all of this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not usually a\Nfan of ponies,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.88,0:01:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but draining your\Nprecious world of magic
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so she could trap the six\Nof you was inspiring!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.82,0:01:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... there's\Nseven of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew we shouldn't have left!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But Starlight's in\Ncharge at the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If anypony can stop\NCozy Glow, it's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Tirek: Cozy Glow\Noutsmarted the six of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt this "Starlight"\Nstands a chance. [cough]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.01,0:01:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Our students can't\Nhandle Cozy on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I guess we'll just\Nhave to bust our way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[groan] That didn't work. [groan]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everything can be\Nsolved with brute force.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We need magic to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's a way to\Nget out without magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a secret lever,\Nor a secret button,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,or a secret admirer who knows a\Nsecret about you, but is all,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Your secret's safe with me\Nbecause I put it in Tartarus
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have a key."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The most powerful villains and\Nmonsters of all time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,are trapped here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And without our\Nmagic, so are we.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...These creatures might be\Nlosing their magical powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's still a magic\Nthat makes up what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can borrow\Nsome of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Chancellor Neighsay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You might as well get used\Nto calling me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Headstallion Neighsay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I plan to be here\Nfor quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:03:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, it sure is a relief\Nto have somepony in charge,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,what with the magical\Ncrisis going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're all so grateful to\Nyou for taking care of those..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,non-ponies, but doesn't\Nthe EEA need you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What the EEA needs is somepony\Nto protect this school
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,from the threats at\NEquestria's borders
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of gallivanting off\Non adventures beyond them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight didn't just\Nrun off willy-nilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She left ME in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm her right-hoof-mare!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Another in a long\Nlist of mistakes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the "Princess of\NFriendship" has made.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest assured, from now on this\Nschool shall be run
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,according to strict\NEEA guidelines...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the way it always\Nshould have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that sounds just peachy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...Headstallion Neighsay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle: Cozy Glow did\Nall of this? How? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but\Ncome on, y'all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta get Starlight out of\Nthere before she comes back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandbar: Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,HELP!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's gotta be what's sucking\Nup all the magic in Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that's true, then\NTwilight and the others
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,went to Tartarus for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And if all of Equestria's magic\Nis getting sucked up in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no way for\Nthem to get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But Starlight's trapped here,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's no way to get word\Nto Celestia or anypony else!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we're on our own...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Still locked, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta at least\Ntry to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? If Sandbar's\Nturned his back on us,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,every other pony\Nprobably has too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandbar not turn his back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandbar is our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Did you miss the part where\Nhe said he didn't want
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,anything to do with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he just said that so one\Nof us could be free to snoop
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,around and figure\Nout what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[window opens]\NSandbar: I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds too clever for\Na pony to come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona knew Sandbar\Nwas still our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We all are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Except for Cozy Glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That pony is NOT who\Nwe thought she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one draining\Nmagic out of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll explain on the\Nway, but right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we've gotta get to\NChancellor Neighsay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.17,0:05:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I know he doesn't\Nlike non-ponies,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but if we tell him what's\Ngoing on, he'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're all concerned\Nabout the magic situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but I want to assure you that\Nthis institution is safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,despite the absence\Nof your Headmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As your new Headstallion, let\Nme be the first to say
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that the reign of Princess\NTwilight is OVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, this school will\Nadhere to EEA doctrine
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,as it should have\Nfrom the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chancellor Neighsay,\Nfor that rousing speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're a stallion who\Ntruly believes what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you say this\Nschool will be run
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,according to EEA doctrine,\NI know you mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And.. when you say there won't\Nbe any more lessons
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,from the Princess of Friendship\Nat the School of Friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you mean that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not exact--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But! Twilight decided\Nto run her school
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,outside of the EEA guidelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And even though you\Ntried to stop her,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Princesses Celestia and\NLuna trusted her enough
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I wouldn't say--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So since I know you\Nmean what you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,my question is really\Nfor the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we going to give the pony\Nwho already tried to wreck
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight's school once\N{\i1}another{\i0} chance to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess things will have to stay\Nthe way Twilight wants them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,which includes\Nleaving me in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All: Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Neighsay: I can-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, so maybe we need a new plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, not too tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want to\Nhurt the Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Twilight will\Nknow what to do with him
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,when she gets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, back to class everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We've let the EEA disrupt our\Nfriendship studies long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you wanted\Nto have somepony
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in charge of the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I do! You just aren't\Nthe pony I had in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't very well have the\NEEA running the school
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,if I want to run it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, that's\Njust the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, if there's one\Nthing I've learned here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it's that friendship is the\Nmost powerful thing there is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and as Headmare of the\NSchool of Friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,nopony will have more\Nfriends than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Making me the most\Npowerful pony in Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Cozy Glow.\NWhat's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just happy to\Nbe running the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm just keeping\NTwilight's seat warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it's pretty impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything\Nwe can do to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We can hang out with\Nyou all day if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there is\Nsomething I need help with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Whoo-hoo! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you've\Nall come to gloat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, we've come to undo\Nall these chains and free you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But.. why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that nasty pony\Nmet even nastier pony,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe nasty pony\Nnot be so nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.23,0:09:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, we'd kinda\Nlike to stop Cozy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,before she drains all the\Nmagic from Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She's behind that as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I must get word to\NCelestia and Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How? Without magic, it'll\Ntake forever to get to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,While it's true that unicorns\Nhave lost their ability
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to cast spells, the most\Npotent magic in Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is housed in our... artifacts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The EEA medallion allows me to\Ntravel throughout Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Its magic worked when\NI chained you up,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps it still has enough\Nto send me to the Princesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he makes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he doesn't come\Nback and lock us up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.51,0:10:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If{\i0} he comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's\Ngonna be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight and the others are\Nprobably already on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure there's\Nmagic in Cerberus?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Clarissa the pig has two tails,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and while her singing\Nvoice is lovely,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think\Nit's magical.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to try everything if\Nwe want to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know;\NTartarus isn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I could hang out\Nhere for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh. Maybe not\Nforever, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tirek: But that is just\Nwhat it will be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If my protege has followed my\Ninstructions, by sunset tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,every last vestige\Nof Equestrian magic
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:11:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,will disappear into\Nthe ether.. FOREVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you even thought about\Nwhat losing magic would mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It means the six of you will be\Ntrapped here, like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It means you're trapped here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever. With US.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh.. I hadn't thought\Nof it like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do we do, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash and Applejack nearly\Nhave Cerberus tired out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If Rarity pitches in, I think\Nthey can get him to sit still
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,long enough to try\Nwhat I have in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I can get the\Nother monsters to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I would NEVER\Ncall them monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Tirek?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably got\Nsome magic too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dooowwwn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to show Equestria\Nthat you aren't "monsters"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wonderful,\Nmystical creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I know it's not{\i0}\N{\i1} your birthday so, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ you get a party{\i0}\N{\i1} even though, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ we'll sing and dance{\i0}\N{\i1} from one to ten, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ and then we'll do{\i0}\N{\i1} it all again! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,More tea, Princess Pudding Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, don't mind if I do!"\NHeh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do this {\i1}all eternity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,FINE! I'll help you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tirek's in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just so excitin' to have\Na foal our age runnin' things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We should have an ice\Ncream social every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a splendid\Nidea, Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But to tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the thing I need help\Nwith most is cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Say no more. Just take\Nus around the school
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and show us everything\Nyou want cleaned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, actually, you can\Nstart right in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks pretty clean already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you three think\Nyou can fool me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a diversion\Nwhen I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Why pony lead us back down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We obviously can't\Nhandle Cozy on our own,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but we can't just sit\Naround and wait for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's one more prisoner\NI think we should free.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! I guess Starlight.\NIs it Starlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Counselor pony come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We need help with nasty pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't talk to\Nus from in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to figure\Na way to get her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! This is just like\Nchapter twelve in
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanthaka's Facts & Artifacts,\Nfrom Twilight's class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I've\Nbeen studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Finals are coming\Nup, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I remember that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Cozy must have linked\Nthese artifacts
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to act like a mystical magnet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,attracting all the magic\Nin Equestria into that orb!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we can shut it down
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,by yanking one of these\Nthings out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, though, that would\Nprobably cause a magical
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,feedback loop and\Ndestroy the whole school!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Cozy: Destroy the\NSchool of Friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor Neighsay was\Nwrong about a lot of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess he was\Nright about all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everypony ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Siiiit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say for how much longer..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,YES, by all means!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just get on with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's your cue, you\Nevil centaur, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think its working!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how\Nlong I can hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully we'll be able to turn\Nyou all back into your normal
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,wonderful selves soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the\Nassist, Your Redness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Twilight did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have done it\Nwithout all your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tirek said all of Equestria's\Nmagic would be gone at sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Without magic, there's\Nno way we'll get back
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to the school in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It means... we failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,After everything\NTwilight's done for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,why would you want\Nto destroy her school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,WE don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.18,0:15:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one using\Nthese artifacts
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to drain magic from Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We all just saw you with\Nyour claws all over them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] It all makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,These creatures want magic\Ngone from Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's the only thing\Nponies have that they don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Technically, there's\Na magical component
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,when Silversteam\Nand I transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And Yona's friends'\Nfriendship IS magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight said!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And you repaid her by\Nsending her to Tartarus
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,on a wild goose chase\Nso you could destroy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,everything she's built!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! They've even trapped\NStarlight in that.. that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to defend the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! Don't listen to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Gallus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They just sacrificed themselves\Ntrying to save their friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Dash always\Nsays there's nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,more loyal than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't {\i1}we{\i0} try to save them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They brought this on themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't seem very\Ngenerous or kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:16:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Elements of Harmony\Nare very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just not applicable\Nin every circumstance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And with magic gone\Nfrom Equestria,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not even sure\Nthe Tree of Harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,will be as helpful\Nas it once was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They're glowing\Nlike the Elements!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the Tree of\NHarmony saved them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess our friendship is\Npretty magical after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, grab the artifacts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... didn't you say that\Ncould DESTROY the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we don't try, we\Ncould lose magic forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You all better get clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Where are you going!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Counselor Pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.. It's nice to see you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess magic is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Cozy: You've\Nruined everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Twilight and her\Nridiculous friends
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,can escape from Tartarus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All my friends are safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can drop the ACT, Cozy Glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your pen pal, Tirek, told us\Nall about how he helped YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,suck up all that magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still don't\Nunderstand why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,WHY!? Because\Nfriendship is power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be the\NPrincess of Friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but as Headmare\Nof this school,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can collect even\Nmore friends than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who\Ndoesn't get it, Cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship IS powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but power isn't why\Nyou make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I couldn't\Nteach you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Gallus: Well, you taught US!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't let one bad apple\Nmake you think you failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And we never could\Nhave stopped her
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,if we hadn't learned what you\Ntaught us about friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Cozy: Honesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Loyalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Generosity?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Blah blah blah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can make more friends\Nwithout using any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I can't do it here,\NI'll do it somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] I'm glad you are\Nback in charge
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of the School of\NFriendship, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's clear to me now that there\Nis no pony better suited
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Headmare Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just practicing\Nfor graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Graduation..?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we've\Nsaved Equestria,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we figured we were\Ndone with school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Saving Equestria is nice, but\NI'm afraid it'll take
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,more than one semester to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,all there is to know\Nabout friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[belch] Told ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,AWWWWWW!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Headmare is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought friendship was\Nsomething that only ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,should share with each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but you all taught\Nme how wrong I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.74,0:20:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose true friendship can\Ntake a lifetime to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were easy to learn,\Nwe wouldn't need a school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[crash] Woah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We held her off as\Nlong as we could!
